      • OldMoveNode

        public OldMoveNode(IEnvironment<T> environment,
                   INode<T> node,
                   IPosition direction,
                   IMolecule movetag)
        Deprecated. 
        Builds a new move node action.
        Parameters:
        environment - The environment where to move
        node - The node to which this action belongs
        direction - The direction where to move
        movetag - A signal molecule which is useful to maintain dependencies among reactions which operate physically on the environment and may be influenced by the move, for instance those conditions that check the number of neighborhoods. If no conditions of this kind are present, just pass null.
